History of the Expedition under the command of Lewis and Clark ... A new edition, faithfully reprinted from the only authorised edition of 1814, with copious critical commentary, prepared upon examination of unpublished official archives, and ... study of the original manuscript journals and field notebooks of the explorers, together with a new biographical and bibliographical introduction, new maps and other illustrations, and a complete index. By Elliot Coues
